---
import PageLayout from "@layouts/PageLayout.astro";
---

<PageLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Compass privacy policy. How we handle your data in compliance with POPIA and South African law."
>
  <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-6">
    Privacy Policy
  </h1>

  <div class="space-y-6 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
    <p>
      <strong class="text-text-primary">Last updated:</strong> January 2025
    </p>

    <p>
      Compass ("we", "us") is committed to protecting your privacy in
      compliance with the Protection of Personal Information Act (POPIA) and
      applicable South African law.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text-primary pt-4">
      What data we collect
    </h2>

    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
      <li>
        <strong class="text-text-primary">Email address:</strong> If you
        subscribe to our mailing list, we collect your email address solely for
        the purpose of sending you new article notifications.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong class="text-text-primary">Analytics data:</strong> We use Google
        Analytics 4 (GA4) to understand how visitors use the site. This
        includes page views, scroll depth, and interaction events.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text-primary pt-4">
      Cookies and consent
    </h2>

    <p>
      GA4 uses cookies to collect analytics data. We implement Google's
      Consent Mode v2, which means:
    </p>

    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
      <li>
        Analytics cookies are <strong class="text-text-primary">not set</strong>
        until you explicitly consent via our cookie banner.
      </li>
      <li>
        If you decline, no analytics cookies are stored and no
        personally identifiable data is collected.
      </li>
      <li>
        You can change your cookie preferences at any time by clicking the
        cookie settings link in the footer.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text-primary pt-4">
      How we use your data
    </h2>

    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
      <li>
        <strong class="text-text-primary">Email:</strong> Used only to send you
        article notifications. We never share your email with third parties.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong class="text-text-primary">Analytics:</strong> Used to understand
        content performance and improve the reading experience. IP addresses
        are anonymised. Data is retained for 2 months.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text-primary pt-4">
      Third-party services
    </h2>

    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
      <li>
        <strong class="text-text-primary">Google Analytics 4:</strong>
        Analytics processing. <a
          href="https://policies.google.com/privacy"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-compass-green underline">Google Privacy Policy</a
        >.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong class="text-text-primary">Buttondown:</strong> Email delivery.
        <a
          href="https://buttondown.email/privacy"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-compass-green underline">Buttondown Privacy Policy</a
        >.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong class="text-text-primary">Netlify:</strong> Hosting and form
        processing. <a
          href="https://www.netlify.com/privacy/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-compass-green underline">Netlify Privacy Policy</a
        >.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text-primary pt-4">
      Data sharing
    </h2>

    <p>
      We do not sell, trade, or share your personal information with third
      parties. Data is only shared with the service providers listed above,
      strictly for the purposes described.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text-primary pt-4">
      Your rights under POPIA
    </h2>

    <p>Under POPIA, you have the right to:</p>

    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
      <li>Request access to your personal information</li>
      <li>Request correction or deletion of your data</li>
      <li>Object to the processing of your personal information</li>
      <li>Withdraw your consent at any time</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      To exercise any of these rights, contact us at
      <strong class="text-text-primary">hello@compass.co.za</strong>.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text-primary pt-4">
      Data retention
    </h2>

    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
      <li>
        <strong class="text-text-primary">Analytics:</strong> 2 months
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong class="text-text-primary">Email addresses:</strong> Retained
        until you unsubscribe
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text-primary pt-4">
      Changes to this policy
    </h2>

    <p>
      We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on
      this page with an updated date.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
